title: Olympic Baby Dreams | Pampers
description:
The Olympic dreams of tomorrow start with a good night’s sleep, thanks to the dryness of Pampers. With three absorbent layers, Pampers diapers keep your future Olympic athlete dry for better sleep and sweeter dreams. 


This Pampers commercial is about your baby's Olympic dreams and a good night's sleep for baby.

transcripts: Maybe he'll win gold in volleyball, maybe weightlifting or soccer but every Olympic dream tomorrow starts with a good nights sleep. Thanks to the overnight dryness of Pampers.  While ordinary diapers have only two layers Pampers have three absorbent layers to stay up to three times drier. For all the dreams of tomorrow wishing you love, sleep, and play Pampers.
